        <h1>Technology</h1>
        <ul>
            <li>ES6 (shared across front and backend) compiled using <a href="https://babeljs.io/">Babel</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">Node.JS</a> for running JS serverside</li>
